-YOU SAID YOUR TETANUS
WAS UP TO DATE.

00:35:00.098 --> 00:35:00.532
-YEP.

00:35:00.532 --> 00:35:04.937
-HIV STATUS AND HEPATITIS B
WILL GET FOLLOWED IN BLOODWORK,

00:35:04.937 --> 00:35:09.708
