-IF IT WAS HIGH-RISK,

00:35:23.021 --> 00:35:26.257
I'D HAVE TO GO
ON THE ANTI-RETROVIRALS

00:35:26.257 --> 00:35:27.492
AND MEDICATIONS TO STOP,

00:35:27.492 --> 00:35:29.962
