00:35:29.962 --> 00:35:32.998
SENDING MY BLOOD TO THE LAB

00:35:32.998 --> 00:35:36.434
TO GET TESTED
FOR HIV,

00:35:36.434 --> 00:35:39.071
HEP C, AND HEP B.

