00:35:49.815 --> 00:35:53.785
I MEAN, IT'S UNFORTUNATELY
A HAZARD OF THE JOB.

00:35:53.785 --> 00:35:54.552
I MEAN, THIS IS SOMETHING

00:35:54.552 --> 00:35:58.090
THAT CAN'T REALLY BE PREDICTED
OR PREVENTED.

00:35:58.090 --> 00:36:08.433
IT HAPPENS.

