-THE EMERGENCY DEPARTMENT
IS KIND OF A LIVE ENTITY.

00:36:11.937 --> 00:36:14.272
IT'S ALMOST
A BIOLOGICAL SYSTEM,

00:36:14.272 --> 00:36:15.674
WITH MULTIPLE DIFFERENT PATIENTS

00:36:15.674 --> 00:36:20.012
THAT YOU'RE MANAGING
OR CARING FOR AT THE SAME TIME.

00:36:20.012 --> 00:36:22.914
SOMEBODY MIGHT BE RECEIVING
IV ANTIBIOTICS

00:36:22.914 --> 00:36:23.648
FOR SEVERE PNEUMONIA.

00:36:23.648 --> 00:36:28.020
SOMEBODY MIGHT BE INVESTIGATED
FOR A POTENTIAL HEART ATTACK,

00:36:28.020 --> 00:36:30.622
AND SO THAT SORT
OF DYNAMIC WORLD

00:36:30.622 --> 00:36:32.256
IS VERY UNIQUE
TO EMERGENCY MEDICINE,

00:36:32.256 --> 00:36:48.506
AND I THINK IT SETS IT APART
FROM OTHER FIELDS OF MEDICINE.

00:36:48.506 --> 00:36:52.010
-TWO STABBING VICTIMS,
10, 20 MINUTES OUT.

