-A HEADS-UP

00:37:06.992 --> 00:37:08.727
THAT WE'VE GOT TWO TRAUMAS
COMING IN,

00:37:08.727 --> 00:37:10.996
ONE OF THEM
DEFINITELY BY CHOPPER.

