-NOW WE'RE GOING TO CALL IN

00:37:18.870 --> 00:37:20.138
OUR COLLEAGUES
FROM THE TRAUMA SERVICE

00:37:20.138 --> 00:37:23.575
AND THE RESIDENT TEAM
TO COME AND HELP US OUT.

